Package: mautu
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: MAUTU Contributors <mautu@example.com>
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-pip, python3-venv
Description: MAUTU - IT Manual Viewer
 A desktop application for browsing, searching, and managing IT manuals.
 Manuals are stored in a local SQLite database and organized by category
 (DevOps, Network, Development). The application is built with PySide6.
